Purpose:
========

Control of multiple 16 bit linear handlers

***************************************************************************


Change Log:
===========


---------------------------------------------------------------------------

Version: 0.00 Mon 03-Jun-96        Alan Glover                   

Was previously named Audio Manager. Renamed to avoid clash with
unregistered third party module of same name.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

Version: 0.01 Tue 18-Jun-96        Alan Glover                   

Preserve condition code on normal exits. Allow 0/-1 combination on
register/activate handler call to parallel SoundDMA's operation.
